import React from 'react'; import Dashboard1 from './components/Dashboard1'; import Dashboard2 from './components/Dashboard2'; import Dashboard3 from './components/Dashboard3'; import FlutterDashboard1 from './components/FlutterDashboard1'; import FlutterDashboard2 from './components/FlutterDashboard2'; import FlutterDashboard3 from './components/FlutterDashboard3'; /** * ReSpace Design System Showcase * * Main App component displaying all dashboard variations * Each dashboard represents a different approach to the home screen */ function App() { return (
{/* Header */}

ReSpace Dashboard Concepts

Multiple unique approaches to the client dashboard for an AI-powered interior design app. Each design follows the warm, material-focused design system with Flutter Material Design principles.

{/* Section: Client Dashboard Screens */}

Client Dashboard - Flutter Material Design

{/* Flutter Dashboard Row 1: Metrics Focus */}

Flutter Version 1: Metrics-Focused Layout

Card-rich design emphasizing progress tracking and data visualization. Clean hierarchy with neumorphic cards and clear metrics display.

{/* Flutter Dashboard Row 2: Activity Feed */}

Flutter Version 2: Widget-Based Activity Feed

Modular widgets with real-time activity updates and performance insights. Dense information display with Material Design elevation patterns.

{/* Flutter Dashboard Row 3: Hero Content */}

Flutter Version 3: Hero Content with Project Carousel

Visual-first approach with gradient hero section and swipeable project cards. Emphasizes large imagery with Material Design elevation and glassmorphic overlays.

{/* Divider */}
{/* Section: Original Interior Design Dashboards */}

Original Interior Design Dashboard Concepts

{/* Dashboard Row 1: Gallery-First */}

Version 1: Gallery-First Approach

Emphasizes visual inspiration with recent designs prominently displayed. Quick access to generate new designs with minimal friction.

{/* Dashboard Row 2: Project-Focused */}

Version 2: Project-Focused Approach

Organization-first design showing active projects with progress tracking. Structured navigation with clear categorization.

{/* Dashboard Row 3: AI-Guided Discovery */}

Version 3: AI-Guided Discovery

Intelligent, personalized recommendations powered by AI. Emphasizes exploration with curated suggestions based on user behavior.

{/* Design System Notes */}

Design System Highlights

Color Palette

  • • Warm cream base (#F8F6F3)
  • • Terracotta accent (#C1694F)
  • • Natural, earthy tones
  • • High contrast for accessibility

Neumorphism

  • • Warm-toned shadows
  • • Cream highlights, gray depth
  • • Material, tactile feel
  • • Cards feel like paper/fabric

Motion

  • • Weighted, deliberate timing
  • • 300ms standard transitions
  • • Reduced spring animations
  • • Feels substantial, not zippy
); } export default App;
